title: JAN 24 2022 - PRES. BIDEN MAY SEND THOUSANDS OF U.S. TROOPS TO RUSSIAN BORDER
description:
Biden’s Administration is continuing to bang the war drums in Ukraine, and now Germany and France will be holding independent talks with Russia outside of the E.U. and without the U.S. There were massive pro-life AND anti-mandate marches held over the weekend in DC and they were INCREDIBLE, now corporate sponsors for the Beijing Olympics are pulling out in a massive win for freedom, plus the CCP’s Huawei paid Tony Podesta $1 million to lobby the Biden White House.

Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
